alerts.title: Wind Advisory
alerts.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM EDT THIS EVENING... ...HIGH WIND WARNING IS CANCELLED... The National Weather Service in Upton has issued a Wind Advisory, which is in effect until 6 PM EDT this evening. The High Wind Warning has been cancelled. * WHAT...West winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph. * WHERE...Entire Tri-State Area. * WHEN...Until 6 PM EDT this evening. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds may blow down limbs, trees, and power lines. Scattered power outages are possible.
